    Tarantulas coughed as he made his way into the smokey clearing where the 
survivors of he Cave explosion and Phobia's crash rested. He could call Black 
Aracnia and tell them that HE had found them....but first he would talk to 
them.
    He made his way into the clearing a looked to the bots. "Well, arent we 
having good luck today? Hehehhehehehehe!" He chuckled. Then the spider 
approached Kitkat.
    "Commander Kitkat, I am acting as Ambassador for my fraction right now. 
And, my fraction is wondering if you are or are not going to join us?"
